{"tid":1381,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[網球] 靜待2017賽季來臨","createTime":"2016-11-25T16:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T15:12:29.000Z","uid":9291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"459793bb35ee3ceadb0be5beabde53ee266710fe","tid":1381,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:15:41.000Z","msg":"頂住檔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc4f75cd7339444afcaefcc88069bd0a0fd25b8","tid":1381,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:05:25.000Z","msg":"無鍾意網球巴絲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907af045923199390f2d53dbce6edd2624828d97","tid":1381,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:22:35.000Z","msg":"羽毛球有林丹李宗偉的宿敵對決，近年網球壇則是費達拿與拿度。雖然二人近年受傷患及年紀漸大影響表現回落，但仍是球迷心目中最精彩的對碰。正在養傷的費達拿就認為拿度及佐高域的存在正是自己的推動力，不認同有指「費達拿若無拿度可贏廿個大滿貫」之說。<br />\n<br />\n拿度在大滿貫決賽曾6度擊敗費達拿，當中包括4次法網、1次溫布頓及1次澳網。<br />\n<br />\n胡比治：拿度令費達拿少贏3個大滿貫<br />\n<br />\n澳洲雙打網球名宿胡比治日前大讚費達拿（Roger Federer）是史上最佳球手，又稱若沒有拿度（Rafael Nadal）的話費天王可獨取廿個大滿貫，多於現時的17個。35歲的費達拿在2003年首奪大滿貫，至2009年完成稱霸4大滿貫，不過自2012年溫布頓後便未嘗大滿貫冠軍。在今年溫布頓4強出局後休戰的費天王接受網球網站《Baseline》訪問時，指就算沒有拿度及佐高域（Novak Djokovic）也只會取得相同的錦標︰<br />\n<br />\n若他們不存在，會有其他好手挑戰。或許其他人不會如二人般推動我至今天的成就，我不知道如何解釋，但相信無論如何我也會保持相同的冠軍。"},{"pid":"b872027068b0a2a3b2d8532a4e54540fde99d2c5","tid":1381,"uid":9344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7d92a77e89de403dad27c03873b0dd2cea614e","tid":1381,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n❤️❤️歡迎❤️❤️"},{"pid":"99d97c1bae3006e7c220779253f7d7dd01e0c210","tid":1381,"uid":7494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T02:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482a9055b6ebf3282c18509b8a2a0166044d1280","tid":1381,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65cd9d2315cea5a27c93959af9ca6b3675ac5d03","tid":1381,"uid":24328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:55:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514822f90accfa8124ef410739016c590daee9ea","tid":1381,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:35:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fd42f0b0e71f5895520b4c1de4d87c62b68553","tid":1381,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:00:54.000Z","msg":"迪普祖退出AO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c627953f59e8e7977d538fa1a6dbd30a1cd07a","tid":1381,"uid":41083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:07:29.000Z","msg":"老費幾時復出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a64553b82ea14fcc602dd77b587a7c83ce4ac5","tid":1381,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老費幾時復出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1月2 賀文盃<br />\nnow tv會播"},{"pid":"ee99d99c71b89583c4fa38dc496f708a6ce3b212","tid":1381,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:32:40.000Z","msg":"有無人睇緊阿布扎比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65e8ca47d47d5500eac77d46ce5e4b4541ab9db","tid":1381,"uid":